title: VA Central Texas Health Care | Austin Veterans Day Celebration & Resource Fair | Veterans Affairs
text:
Austin Veterans Day Celebration & Resource Fair
Veterans Day Celebration and Resource Fair
When:
Wed. Nov 13, 2024, 10:00 am – 2:00 pm CT
Where:
Cost:
Free
Seating is limited. Parking will be validated with registration.
In lieu of the monthly benefits clinic normally held at the Austin Outpatient Clinic, join your VA team at the 2024 City of Austin Veterans Day Celebration & Resource Fair where Veterans can connect with local, state and federal organizations offering support, resources, and services tailored to their needs.
• Receive valuable information on topics such as disability compensation, healthcare, educational services, and more.
• The event is no cost and open to the public.
• Lunch provided.
